We also cover ALL of our top TIPS for DIY yogurt success, so be sure to check out the full post via the LINK in our bio! #yogurt #plantbased #probiotics #coconutyogurt

node.text: Ever wondered how to make COCONUT WHIPPED CREAM🤔? The struggle can be real, but we’re showing you our foolproof methods for PERFECT coconut whip every time😋! We share tips, tricks, and detail exactly what coconut cream brands will set you up for success🥥🥛. Read our STEP-BY-STEP methods via the LINK in our bio! #howto #whippedcream #plantbased #dessert⁠

node.title: How To Make Coconut Whipped Cream

node.text:
Ever tried spaghetti squash? Our NEW Spaghetti Squash Stir-Fry is a hearty, delicious way to enjoy it! 🤩 Think: squash "noodles" combined with colorful vegetables 🫑🧅, flavorful baked tofu, & the best stir-fry sauce you've ever tried 🥜...& just 10 simple INGREDIENTS to make it! // LINK in bio for the recipe!⁠⁠

#spaghettisquash #stirfry #easyveganrecipes #vegandinnerideas

node.text:
Ever crave cake for breakfast? 🎂 Well, today we've got you covered 😉 Our Red Velvet 🌹 Cake Smoothie is SIMPLE, captures alll those red velvet flavors you love 😍, and is 100% acceptable for any meal of the day! 🙌🏻 Get your blenders ready for this delicious smoothie! 🥤⁠⁠
⁠⁠
Find the recipe here: minimalistbaker.com/red-velvet-cake-smoothie/⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#redvelvet #redvelvetcake #redvelvetsmoothie #vegansmoothie #smoothierecipes #healthysmoothies #easyveganrecipes #veganbreakfast

node.text:
We all love desserts...but in the summer heat, honestly who wants to *bake* anything? 🥵 Today we're bringing you 56 EASY NO-bake (plant-based!) desserts to satisfy your cravings, sans-oven! 🙌🏻🍰 From easy brownie bites, to no-bake cookies, to vegan cheesecakes galore, get your sweet tooth on with our decadent treats that are SUPER simple to make! // LINK in bio for the full round-up!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#nobakedesserts #nobake #easyvegandesserts #easyveganrecipes

NEW! You saw our new Whole-Grain Pancake mix...but did you think we'd forget about our GF friends? Never! 😉 Our GF Pancake Mix is equally EASY, delicious, and makes the most FLUFFY ☁️, wholesome pancakes! 🥞 Get your weekend plates ready and whip some up today! 🍁 // LINK in bio for the recipe!⁠⁠
⁠⁠
#pancakes #veganpancakes #gfpancakes #glutenfreepancakes #glutenfreebreakfast #glutenfreebaking
